data.description: Highly desirable neighborhood in Moody, AL! Here's the perfect family home that's turnkey and ready for you! Split bedrooms, LVP flooring and fresh paint are just a few features you will enjoy. The backyard has a patio-pavered fire-pit and fenced for privacy where you can enjoy evenings with friends and family. Make your appointment now for when showings are available.
